Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.54,0:03:10.54,OP_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,------------------- OP heroine frame -------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.70,0:03:15.81,OP_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{be2\fad(100,100)}数十億もの 鼓動の数さえ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.99,0:03:22.66,OP_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{be2\fad(100,100)}貴方には瞬き程度の些事な等級
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.82,0:03:27.65,OP_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{be2\fad(100,100)}過去に因われて未来を嘆くも
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.88,0:03:33.53,OP_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{be2\fad(100,100)}塵一つ誤算を許さぬ必然
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.89,0:03:39.88,OP_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{be2\fad(100,100)}無限に広がる夢も 描く未来も
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.09,0:03:45.49,OP_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{be2\fad(100,100)}僕たちに許された虚栄の権利
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.74,0:03:51.64,OP_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{be2\fad(100,100)}有限 それは二つの針が示す
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.87,0:03:56.53,OP_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{be2\fad(100,100)}残酷な約定と選択へ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.72,0:03:58.69,OP_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{be2\fad(100,100)}Hacking to the Gate
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.02,0:04:05.67,OP_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{be2\fad(100,100)}だから今 一秒ごとに世界線を越えて
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.88,0:04:10.77,OP_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{be2\fad(100,100)}君のその笑顔 守りたいのさ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.94,0:04:17.64,OP_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{be2\fad(100,100)}そしてまた 悲しみのない時間のループへと
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.81,0:04:23.95,OP_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{be2\fad(100,100)}飲み込まれていく 孤独の観測者
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.70,0:03:15.81,OP_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{be2\fad(100,100)}就连数十亿生物的鼓动之数
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.99,0:03:22.66,OP_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2\fad(100,100)}也不过如对你眨眼般琐碎的等级
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.82,0:03:27.65,OP_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{be2\fad(100,100)}即使叹息囚禁于过去的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.88,0:03:33.53,OP_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{be2\fad(100,100)}也无法容许微小误算的必然
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.89,0:03:39.88,OP_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{be2\fad(100,100)}无限扩展的梦想 描绘而出的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.09,0:03:45.49,OP_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2\fad(100,100)}都是我们被允许的虚荣权利
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.74,0:03:51.64,OP_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{be2\fad(100,100)}有限 此为两支时针所昭示的真实
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.87,0:03:56.53,OP_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{be2\fad(100,100)}指向残酷的约定与选择
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.72,0:03:58.69,OP_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{be2\fad(100,100)}Hacking to the Gate
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.02,0:04:05.67,OP_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{be2\fad(100,100)}所以此刻 只凭一秒即可穿越世界线
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.88,0:04:10.77,OP_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{be2\fad(100,100)}想要守护你的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.94,0:04:17.64,OP_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{be2\fad(100,100)}然后再次 去往没有悲伤的时间轮回
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.81,0:04:23.95,OP_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{be2\fad(100,100)}逐渐吞噬消失 孤独的观测者
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.77,0:00:04.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间机器由SERN回收
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.44,0:00:06.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SERN? 怎么回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.90,0:00:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牧瀬红莉栖 冈部伦太郎 桥田至
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.70,0:00:14.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们三个人也一起跟着走一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.16,0:00:19.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真…真由理呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.37,0:00:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,椎名真由理…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.08,0:00:26.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不需要的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.50,0:00:30.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.05,0:00:34.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.26,0:00:39.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了FB FB…FB
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.75,0:01:03.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由理
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.46,0:01:05.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由理!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.42,0:01:10.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由理
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.22,0:01:18.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这算什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.81,0:01:27.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.23,0:01:33.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冈部! 快放手!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.53,0:01:35.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否则你也会被杀掉的!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.74,0:01:40.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.66,0:01:42.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我绝对不原谅那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.36,0:02:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,42
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.98,0:02:16.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,显像管
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.69,0:02:18.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经开启
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.16,0:02:26.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.46,0:02:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冈部
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.42,0:02:37.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.63,0:02:40.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 如果失败的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.09,0:02:41.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我快点!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.26,0:02:46.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冈部
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.89,0:02:52.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跳跃吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.99,0:04:32.00,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(779,652)}形而上的坏死
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.09,0:04:35.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由理祖母去世的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.91,0:04:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她还是个小学生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.70,0:04:44.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由理每天都会去墓前祭拜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.03,0:04:49.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自从祖母去世后 持续了有半年之久
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.16,0:04:53.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿着遗物怀表
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.42,0:04:57.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直抬头仰望天空
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.10,0:05:03.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像在等待祖母迎接
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.65,0:05:08.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而某一天 突然光芒四射
