Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.65,0:05:20.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也被称作「天使的阶梯」的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.28,0:05:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由理就好像正在被那光芒吞噬
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.74,0:05:31.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就好像这样下去 真由理就会消失一样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.26,0:05:33.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由理!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.75,0:05:38.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冈伦?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.74,0:05:41.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会让你被带走的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.15,0:05:43.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由理是我的人质
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.36,0:05:47.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是人体实验的样品
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.82,0:05:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脱口而出的 是小时候学会的那些台词
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.95,0:05:55.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和真由理一起看的一部电视剧中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.87,0:06:00.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,科学狂人像疯子一样喊出的台词
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.88,0:06:03.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.21,0:06:06.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由喜是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.67,0:06:09.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冈伦的人质啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.18,0:06:15.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那就没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.28,0:06:33.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.87,0:06:37.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说在打瞌睡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.38,0:06:49.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在几点?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.71,0:06:51.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,几点!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.63,0:06:52.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.13,0:06:54.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快五点了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.97,0:06:56.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是要去买东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.22,0:06:58.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,买东西?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.22,0:07:01.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就去订披萨了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.77,0:07:02.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.68,0:07:04.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别点热带水果特制披萨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.64,0:07:05.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃不了那个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.85,0:07:07.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.81,0:07:11.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间跳跃 成功了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.61,0:07:12.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冈部
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.53,0:07:13.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由理呢?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.69,0:07:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由理在哪!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.95,0:07:16.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了啊 突然问这个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.24,0:07:18.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由氏的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.28,0:07:22.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是刚刚去邀请琉华氏参加Party了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.87,0:07:25.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去买东西?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.87,0:07:27.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开发评议会中止
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.92,0:07:29.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中止? 为什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.67,0:07:30.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.09,0:07:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就此解散
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.76,0:07:35.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们俩都赶快回家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.88,0:07:36.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.63,0:07:37.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了! 快回去!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.80,0:07:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听到了吗! 一定要回去!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.01,0:07:42.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.76,0:07:44.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就是接了一下手机嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.06,0:07:48.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手机?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.52,0:07:54.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘟嘟噜 这里是真由喜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.61,0:07:57.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在无法接听电话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.36,0:07:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有事…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.60,0:08:05.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看样子世界线并没有发生巨大改变
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.86,0:08:07.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和发送D-MAIL的时候不同
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.04,0:08:10.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次是真的回到了今天5点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.83,0:08:15.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咔嗒咔嗒 新干线
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.05,0:08:19.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对吧 新干线是白色的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.52,0:08:24.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这之后 真由理会带着铃羽回来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.92,0:08:28.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该去报警吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.83,0:08:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 谁会相信啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.38,0:08:33.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从未来时间跳跃回来这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.30,0:08:36.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在剩下的三小时内必须得做些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.64,0:08:40.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由理! 真由理!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.97,0:08:44.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冈…不 凶真…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.23,0:08:45.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由理在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.19,0:08:47.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.77,0:08:49.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去了? 什么时候?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.31,0:08:52.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概30分钟之前吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.32,0:08:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是回Lab去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.65,0:08:56.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道她还没回去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.82,0:08:58.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.61,0:09:01.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她特地来邀请我去参加Party
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.49,0:09:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我今天实在是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.20,0:09:05.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她有没有说会顺路去哪?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.29,0:09:08.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由理酱吗? 没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.12,0:09:11.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果看到她的话 立刻给我打电话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.59,0:09:13.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.34,0:09:16.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然世界线没有变化 也就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.47,0:09:19.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由理自身的活动
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.39,0:09:21.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我不去影响是不会改变的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.85,0:09:23.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.89,0:09:28.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喵喵 菲利斯现在不能接电话喵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.73,0:09:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.07,0:09:38.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由理你到底在哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.20,0:09:41.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由理吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.16,0:09:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不巧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.16,0:09:44.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,助手吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.95,0:09:47.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不说过今天解散了吗 你快点…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.41,0:09:48.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老实回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.87,0:09:51.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是从未来时间跳跃回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.71,0:09:57.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么知道的?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.42,0:09:59.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你从接手机的那一瞬间起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.39,0:10:01.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像整个人都变了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.85,0:10:04.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你这样子 应该是发生了什么事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.48,0:10:08.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是没时间跟你详细说明了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.19,0:10:10.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之你先逃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.56,0:10:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃? 逃去哪啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.48,0:10:15.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪都行 尽可能远离Lab
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.82,0:10:16.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.49,0:10:19.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过后要好好解释清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.45,0:10:21.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 也替我转告桶子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.03,0:10:22.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.70,0:10:24.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冈部
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.79,0:10:25.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.33,0:10:28.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要做傻事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.38,0:10:31.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.00,0:10:36.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冈部伦太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.80,0:10:38.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个啊 泡茶的水…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.34,0:10:39.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看到过真由理吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.55,0:10:42.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,椎名真由理?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.47,0:10:45.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 刚才正好在邀请我去参加Party呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.14,0:10:46.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.10,0:10:47.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那里右转…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.14,0:10:51.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 泡茶的水到底在哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.40,0:10:54.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绹想去买东西 我得送她过去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.52,0:10:55.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要问路的话去派出所
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.11,0:10:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 送她过去后你也别回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.70,0:11:00.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.32,0:11:01.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原因之后再说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.71,0:11:18.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由理
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.22,0:11:20.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由理
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.38,0:11:21.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 冈伦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.14,0:11:24.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看 是一番星哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.43,0:11:25.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.89,0:11:27.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别问了 和我一起走
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.89,0:11:29.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎? Party呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.73,0:11:30.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不办了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.15,0:11:32.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经跟克里斯和桶子说过了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.81,0:11:34.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎? 为什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.52,0:11:35.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后我再解释
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.98,0:11:38.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我都邀请铃小姐了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.36,0:11:40.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有桶子君也订了披萨
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.03,0:11:41.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了 按我说的做!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.99,0:11:44.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冈伦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.16,0:11:47.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.46,0:11:53.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由喜不明白啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.50,0:11:56.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然你经常做一些莫名其妙的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.21,0:12:00.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但今天的你是真的莫名其妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.38,0:12:05.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是想进行实验吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.31,0:12:06.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由理
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.60,0:12:12.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.56,0:12:15.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 现在能按我说的做吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.15,0:12:18.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.44,0:12:21.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后我会跟你详细说明的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.78,0:12:25.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 抱歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.45,0:12:27.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由喜只是有点吃惊罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.12,0:12:29.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.12,0:12:31.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没有错
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.63,0:12:41.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好多人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.59,0:12:43.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这时候是回家高峰期啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.85,0:12:48.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦? 但是大厅里一个人都没有哎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.10,0:12:51.44,Default_tip,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再通知一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.98,0:12:53.52,Default_tip,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由于出现了爆炸预告
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.56,0:12:56.57,Default_tip,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在暂时停止运行的路线如下所示
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.71,0:12:58.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz18\fs38\bord0\be1\1c&H3D3D37&\pos(463,313)}由于出现了爆炸的恐怖预告
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.71,0:12:58.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz18\fs38\bord0\be1\1c&H3D3D37&\pos(580,431)}现在警视厅 铁路警察正在调查可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.71,0:12:58.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz18\fs38\bord0\be1\1c&H3D3D37&\pos(678,440)}物品，以下所有线路暂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.71,0:12:58.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz18\fs38\bord0\be1\1c&H3D3D37&\pos(584,508)}时停运
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.81,0:12:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说还没有恢复运行的迹象啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.40,0:13:00.57,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 讨厌死了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.82,0:13:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么会犯这种低级错误
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.99,0:13:02.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这种时候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.11,0:13:03.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冈伦?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.03,0:13:03.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由理
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.74,0:13:05.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去地铁 快点…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.03,0:13:08.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是冈部伦太郎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.08,0:13:13.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.42,0:13:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我走一趟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.30,0:13:21.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边傻站着干嘛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.17,0:13:21.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让开
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.01,0:13:23.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.35,0:13:33.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑起来 拼命跑起来!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.06,0:13:37.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那群人是?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.19,0:13:40.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冈伦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.15,0:13:41.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你快走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.53,0:13:42.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃 真由理
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.80,0:14:05.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死掉的是椎名真由理
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.18,0:14:07.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冈部君…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.35,0:14:10.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 冈部伦太郎被捕获了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.81,0:14:11.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由理
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.85,0:14:15.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.56,0:14:16.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会让你死的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.69,0:14:19.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由理 我一定会救你的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.78,0:14:23.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救你…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.70,0:14:29.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.21,0:14:39.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中止? 为什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.13,0:14:40.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事了?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.55,0:14:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 其实…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.34,0:14:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得到了今晚Mr.显像管会来的消息
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.35,0:14:51.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冈伦 你又搞出什么事了?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.43,0:14:53.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 稍微有点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.60,0:14:54.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是真由理呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.64,0:14:56.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会跟真由理说的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.44,0:14:58.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之留在这里很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.11,0:15:00.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就此解散吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.61,0:15:04.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太强硬了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.07,0:15:09.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 就算可疑也好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.08,0:15:11.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之现在…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.70,0:15:13.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须让大家远离Lab
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.37,0:15:17.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘟嘟噜 这里是真由喜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.54,0:15:19.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不能接电话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.88,0:15:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何都会很花时间
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.30,0:15:28.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话就跟刚才一样了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.22,0:15:29.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须得做点什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.94,0:15:37.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.23,0:15:39.65,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琉华子 是我 冈部
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.81,0:15:41.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冈…不 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.73,0:15:42.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是凶真先…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.86,0:15:42.48,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由理呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.65,0:15:43.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.07,0:15:44.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由理在你那边吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.19,0:15:45.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由理酱吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.24,0:15:47.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 她现在正想回去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.05,0:15:49.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我叫住她
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.34,0:15:52.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我过来之前 绝对不要让她离开
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.94,0:15:54.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是她说要回Lab…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.34,0:15:56.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了 按我说的做
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.59,0:15:57.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.89,0:15:59.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由理酱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.56,0:16:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咔嗒咔嗒 新干线
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.53,0:16:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对吧 新干线是白色的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.70,0:16:11.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由理
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.41,0:16:15.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 冈伦 嘟嘟噜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.17,0:16:19.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.67,0:16:23.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正准备修补好吹雪酱的COS服就回Lab呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.88,0:16:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吹雪酱? 是一起COSPLAY的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.43,0:16:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 她说真由喜做的COS服的线头散了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.18,0:16:32.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚收到了邮件
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.14,0:16:34.27,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这么一回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.48,0:16:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等修补好了 马上就回Lab
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.90,0:16:38.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定能赶上Party的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.52,0:16:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢着 Party…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.69,0:16:41.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Party中…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.40,0:16:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,延期了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.40,0:16:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎? 为什么啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.45,0:16:48.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为Lab暂时无法使用了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.62,0:16:50.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.66,0:16:53.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.20,0:16:56.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 我希望你能陪我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.29,0:16:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是现在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.58,0:16:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吹雪酱呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.50,0:17:01.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 不过这事得先放一放
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.46,0:17:02.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十万火急
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.67,0:17:04.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…发生什么事了啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.13,0:17:07.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 接下来我们要出趟远门
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.68,0:17:09.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.47,0:17:12.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎哎? 就你们两个人?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.56,0:17:13.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.47,0:17:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 吹雪酱那边明天也能去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.15,0:17:19.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过真是突然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.52,0:17:20.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去哪里呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.86,0:17:22.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个之后再说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.69,0:17:24.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快没时间搭电车了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.48,0:17:28.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是真由喜什么都没准备啊 钱也…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.28,0:17:29.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些你不必担心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.28,0:17:31.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.41,0:17:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等啦 冈伦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.04,0:17:36.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.79,0:17:39.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一…一路顺风
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.92,0:17:42.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我们走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.43,0:17:51.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋叶原车站不是在对面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.18,0:17:53.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搭地铁走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.06,0:17:55.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.79,0:18:09.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.89,0:18:15.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经很久没有像这样被冈伦拉着走了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.87,0:18:29.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往回走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.31,0:18:53.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.11,0:18:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz13\fs43\bord0\be1\pos(862,132)}发生什么事了?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.11,0:18:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz13\fs48\bord0\be1\pos(537,324)}之后要给我说明清楚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.90,0:19:01.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红莉栖吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.95,0:19:17.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦? 真由喜的怀表停了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.33,0:19:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪 明明才刚上过发条
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.05,0:19:28.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人还真多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.80,0:19:30.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为总武线停止运行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.47,0:19:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停止运行了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.97,0:19:38.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是接到电话 说有人安装了炸弹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.44,0:19:40.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.98,0:19:45.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 冈伦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.07,0:19:48.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.53,0:19:52.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由喜虽然有一肚子疑问
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.16,0:19:53.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我现在会忍住的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.16,0:19:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过作为交换
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.75,0:20:00.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到一切都结束的时候 希望你能告诉我全部
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.17,0:20:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我答应你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.68,0:20:12.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.72,0:20:18.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没能帮上你的忙 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.15,0:20:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Party…今后再开吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.95,0:20:31.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 今后…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.25,0:20:41.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后…一定能…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.79,0:20:48.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由理姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.39,0:21:36.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.31,0:21:39.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是故意的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.27,0:21:47.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…只是想…给姐姐一个惊喜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.12,0:21:58.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我绝不会让你死…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.74,0:22:05.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由理…我…一定会救你的!



Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.01,0:22:10.01,ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,------------------- ED first non-black frame -------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.22,0:22:27.82,ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,規制された視界 無慈悲なる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.19,0:22:36.58,ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十二の支配 逃れられない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.83,0:22:45.00,ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安息の明日を願った
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.75,0:22:54.14,ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手の中の尊い事象の地平へ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.34,0:23:02.94,ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,囚われし盟約 現れた偽証の輪郭
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.10,0:23:12.07,ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生命の天地は盲目な時間を刻んで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.28,0:23:17.08,ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羽ばたけバタフライ 奇跡のバタフライ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.45,0:23:20.96,ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あなたへ捧ぐ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.12,0:23:25.34,ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涙のバタフライ 眩しいバタフライ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.50,0:23:32.85,ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全てが 今書き換えられる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.22,0:22:27.82,ED_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被限制的视界 毫无慈悲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.19,0:22:36.58,ED_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十二条的支配 无从逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.83,0:22:45.00,ED_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也曾祈求安息的明日
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.75,0:22:54.14,ED_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去向手中珍贵现象的地平线
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.34,0:23:02.94,ED_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被囚禁的盟约 出现的伪证轮廓
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.10,0:23:12.07,ED_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生命的天地即铭刻于盲目的时间之中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.28,0:23:17.08,ED_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振翅高飞吧蝴蝶 奇迹的蝴蝶
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.45,0:23:20.96,ED_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向你奉献一切
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.12,0:23:25.34,ED_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泪水闪耀的蝴蝶 炫目的蝴蝶
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.50,0:23:32.85,ED_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此刻 能将一切重写
